    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0774c09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013158">杭州<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz23"/>秦<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz23"/>望山</placeName><persName key="A010492">圓脩</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0774c10"/><persName key="A010492">釋圓脩</persName>姓潘氏，<placeName key="PL000000017166">福州閩</placeName>人也。生而<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz24"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz24"/>嶷，長而<lb
ed="T" n="0774c11"/>俊邁。忽思拔俗，尋事名師，剔髮變衣，年滿，<lb
ed="T" n="0774c12"/>於<placeName key="PL000000023256">嵩陽會善寺</placeName>納戒。既而儀表容與，日新<lb
ed="T" n="0774c13"/>厥德，研窮經論，俄約觀方。遇<placeName key="PL000000019628">百丈山</placeName><persName key="A001897">海禪<lb
ed="T" n="0774c14"/>師</persName>，根教相符，遂明心要。持盃振錫，而抵于<lb
ed="T" n="0774c15"/><placeName key="PL000000011519">杭</placeName>。見<placeName key="PL000000013158">秦望山</placeName>峻極之勢，有長松枝繁結蓋，<lb
ed="T" n="0774c16"/>遂棲止于松巔。時感鵲復巢於橫枝，物我<lb
ed="T" n="0774c17"/>都忘，羽族馴狎。由茲不下，近四十秋。每一<lb
ed="T" n="0774c18"/>太守到任，則就瞻仰，號<persName key="A010492">鳥窠禪師</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0774004"/>焉<anchor xml:id="end0774004"/>。洎<lb
ed="T" n="0774c19"/><date key="j20154742015855" notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" notAfter-iso="+0807-02-14"><name>元和</name>初</date>，邦伯<persName key="A010494">裴常棣</persName>酷重其道，請下結庵者<lb
ed="T" n="0774c20"/>至于三四，或為參請<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz25"/>者<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz25"/>說法，<persName key="A010494">裴侯</persName>命八屬<lb
ed="T" n="0774c21"/>宰官同力造伽藍，移廢額曰「<placeName key="PL000000011491">招賢</placeName>」以居<lb
ed="T" n="0774c22"/><ref type="person" target="#A010492">之</ref><ptr target="#n1480"/>。<date key="j20256222025622" when-iso="+0833-11-11"><anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz26"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz26"/>和七年癸丑歲九月二十二日</date>，端坐，怡<lb
ed="T" n="0774c23"/>然歸寂，享年九十九，僧臘八十。<placeName key="PL000000011519">杭</placeName>之累政良<lb
ed="T" n="0774c24"/>守無不傾重，稅駕樹陰，請談玄極，不覺<lb
ed="T" n="0774c25"/>更僕移辰矣。今塔在<placeName key="PL000000011583">石甑山</placeName>下，<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>僧<persName key="A010493">唯<lb
ed="T" n="0774c26"/>貞</persName>為塔銘焉。近有盜發其塔，且多怪異，止<lb
ed="T" n="0774c27"/>收得銘誌而已。</p>
